data.description: Assumable FHA loan at 5.625% available! Charming 3 bed 2 bath home with your own private pool and fresh interior paint! No HOA! Walk through the front door and relax in your living room that opens into the recently updated kitchen, featuring a desired farmers sink, stainless steel range and refrigerator. From there enjoy entertaining in the family room that exits onto your covered patio overlooking your recently re-surfaced pool. Generously sized lot also has a separate large fenced grass yard for children or pets. Extra storage for belongings in either the included shed or storage closet. Roof replaced 2019 and solar recently added. Great location that provides easy access to freeways.
